{"id":251,"date":"2020-04-03T15:18:40","date_gmt":"2020-04-03T15:18:40","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/?p=251"},"modified":"2020-05-18T13:18:35","modified_gmt":"2020-05-18T13:18:35","slug":"raid-boss-new-alliance-event-type","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/2020\/04\/03\/raid-boss-new-alliance-event-type\/","title":{"rendered":"RAID BOSS &#8211; NEW ALLIANCE EVENT TYPE"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><strong><em>Please note<\/em><\/strong><em>: the information below is not final, and certain aspects may be subject to change before appearing live in-game.&nbsp;<\/em><br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>CONTENTS:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Raid Boss &#8211; New Alliance Event Type<ol><li>Entry Requirements<\/li><li>How to Play<\/li><li>Rewards<\/li><\/ol><\/li><li>Raid Boss Beta &#8211; Zeus, Lord of Olympus<ol><li>Overview<\/li><li>Raid Boss Titan<\/li><li>Alliance Rewards<\/li><\/ol><\/li><li>Feedback and Social Channels<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>RAID BOSS &#8211; NEW ALLIANCE EVENT TYPE<\/strong><br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/ppbK7TOSVhvaOA1AdzdrydwdmdVjiXGAdBy8-4eit_xuys2ZXR2dD8TBha6_sbxOVODtWqI6U-meVbiSKbLwHzW8QS6KfZI9BY8wn8AIahL-7N_2iIDWjGlR8k_IlZa5B2oSH3Hq\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Get ready for a <strong>new Event<\/strong> coming to Dawn of Titans on <strong>Monday 6th April<\/strong>!<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Raid Boss Events are finally here! This new event type requires you and your Alliance to <strong>work together<\/strong> to deal damage to a <strong>Raid Boss Titan<\/strong> over a number of levels of <strong>increasing difficulty<\/strong>, in order to win <strong>powerful Rewards <\/strong>for everyone in your Alliance.<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>ENTRY REQUIREMENTS<\/strong><br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To participate in the event, you must be:<br><br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Castle Level 10<\/strong> and above.<\/li><li>In an <strong>Alliance<\/strong>.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>HOW TO PLAY<\/strong><br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https:\/\/lh6.googleusercontent.com\/9DsBhfinFJT3UqrIM6H6Mb5WgdmRtmG4Ga4LpBDgZ4VAU-DwIQeN8oDjRVcAg1pFYn-xYrTtnttshoFEZ1bQGFde212c3aHUeFgigPyP80frrkcCdpI_Ue50-4kGBTniAEvMfUXy\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>During the Raid Boss Event, you and your Alliance members will be tasked with battling against a <strong>formidable, uniquely-skilled Titan<\/strong> on a <strong>dynamic battlefield,<\/strong> with <strong>Invoke<\/strong> effects, spells and reinforcements standing in your way.<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For each battle, the amount of damage you deal to the Raid Boss Titan\u2019s health gets converted into<strong> Points<\/strong>, which are then added to an <strong>Alliance Total<\/strong>.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once your Alliance reaches a certain number of points, the <strong>Plinth Level<\/strong> of the Raid Boss will increase, triggering a <strong>tougher battle<\/strong> and a new Points total to reach before unlocking the next level.&nbsp;<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Points required to complete each level are:<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>PLINTH LEVEL 1: <strong>150,000<\/strong> Points<\/li><li>PLINTH LEVEL 2: <strong>600,000<\/strong> Points<\/li><li>PLINTH LEVEL 3: <strong>1,500,000<\/strong> Points<\/li><li>PLINTH LEVEL 4: <strong>3,750,000<\/strong> Points<\/li><li>PLINTH LEVEL 5: <strong>5,500,000<\/strong> Points<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>REWARDS<\/strong><br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https:\/\/lh4.googleusercontent.com\/HfS_HxXzgg2R57SLv9zYfyGvwnZmhyCdfY1ZJKI_iBGXRoY-RPCc-I6mqaiF3p6X8XEIYhD2r0qPxTd_vVqe4trQDKUs19y4Udk8R4MwXhtHiFZacZn6X4ZgJEt8d9wsB32CgNQR\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Rewards for participating in a Raid Boss event are granted <strong>at the end of the event. <\/strong>They are given to <strong>all players in the Alliance<\/strong> that met the <strong>entry requirements<\/strong> (Castle Level 10 and in an Alliance) and <strong>achieved at least one Point<\/strong> whilst the event was live. No rewards (aside from battle drops) are given out whilst the event is active.<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Players receive rewards for <strong>each level their Alliance manages to defeat<\/strong> whilst the event is active. For example, if your Alliance reaches Plinth Level 4, but does not complete that level before the event ends, you will receive rewards for Plinth Level 1, 2 and 3.<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Upon conclusion of the event, rewards will appear in each player\u2019s <strong>Treasure Room<\/strong>, ready for collection.<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>RAID BOSS BETA &#8211; ZEUS, LORD OF OLYMPUS<\/strong><br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><em>Please note<\/em><\/strong><em>: this first Raid Boss Event is a <\/em><strong><em>Beta launch<\/em><\/strong><em>, and as such, the rewards, scoring, difficulty and values are not necessarily final, and may be <\/em><strong><em>subject to change<\/em><\/strong><em> before the event goes live, or prior to subsequent Raid Boss Events that follow this Beta.<\/em><br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Overview:<\/strong><br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Event Starts:<\/strong> Monday 6th April at 13:00 PM UTC<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Event Ends:<\/strong> Wednesday 8th April at 12:00 PM UTC<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Zeus, angered by the shift in power since the arrival of the new Gods, descends from his throne on Mount Olympus to reestablish his reign over the Shattered Kingdoms.<\/em><br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>With power never-before-seen, Zeus enters the battlefield with the ability to increase his own strength as his health depletes.<\/em><br><br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Raid Boss Titan:<\/strong><br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Zeus utilises the power of <strong>INVOKE<\/strong> skills to increase his strength in battle <strong>as you deal damage to his health<\/strong>. At various intervals, he invokes the power of the Heavens to <strong>call in reinforcements<\/strong>, <strong>cast lightning spells<\/strong>,<strong> resist spells cast upon him<\/strong> and <strong>increase his own stats<\/strong> with the <strong>WRATH OF ZEUS<\/strong>.<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"436\" height=\"220\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/dot0304_1-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-253\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/dot0304_1-1.png 436w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/dot0304_1-1-300x151.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 436px) 100vw, 436px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Alliance Rewards:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Raid Boss event rewards are centered around giving <strong>maximum boosts<\/strong> for <strong>upcoming leaderboard events<\/strong>.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the Zeus Raid Boss Beta, the <strong>Top Reward<\/strong> is a <strong>4-STAR LEVEL 10 JALDARG<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>JALDARG<\/strong> is the <strong>Top Boost Titan<\/strong> (Chosen Titan of 1.4x) for the <strong>Lithotaur Alliance War<\/strong> starting Thursday 9th April. Alongside him will be<strong> Boost Relics<\/strong> (Earthly Candles) that provide increased numbers of Souls gained per battle for the <strong>Lithotaur Alliance War<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The <strong>Rewards<\/strong> are as follows:<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"277\" height=\"651\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/dot0304_2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-254\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/dot0304_2.png 277w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/dot0304_2-128x300.png 128w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 277px) 100vw, 277px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>FEEDBACK AND SOCIAL CHANNELS<\/strong><br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We want to hear from you! Once the Raid Boss Beta concludes on Wednesday 8th April, please contact us with your feedback via our social channels here:<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/dawnoftitansofficial\/\">Facebook<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/DawnOfTitans\">Twitter<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/dawnoftitans\/\">Instagram<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/dawnoftitans\">YouTube<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>And as always, we\u2019ll <strong><em>see you on the battlefield!<\/em><\/strong><br><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Please note: the information below is not final, and certain aspects may be subject to change before appearing live in-game.&nbsp; CONTENTS: Raid Boss &#8211; New&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":353,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[7],"tags":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/pasted-image-0-5.png","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/251"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=251"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/251\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":354,"href":"https:\/\/blo